    "We first draw the processing state diagram of the enterprises in the experimental group.",
    "Figure 8 shows that the Y coordinate is the code of the listed enterprise.",
    "Dark blue represents the time when the experimental group enterprises issued green bonds.",
    "Light blue represents when the experimental group enterprises have not issued green bonds.",
    "We then divide the enterprises of the original experimental group into two types: (1) early processing, such as enterprise 2202, and (2) late processing, such as enterprise 301."
